{{Flavour|Fires a volley of barbs at the target, skewering them and making movement painful.}}

'''Throw Barbs''' is a monster-only [[spell]] that deals moderate damage and inflicts the [[Barbs]] status, which deals damage every time the target moves. The barbs will wear off faster if you stay in your position.

